---

## 5) API / Model Checklist (Minimum)

Models:
- `User` — auth, profile, pushTokens[]
- `Product` — CRUD, image, category, price
- `Review` — rating, text, linked to User + Product + Order
- `Order` — items, status lifecycle, linked to User
- `NotificationLog` (optional) — track sent promos

Critical backend endpoints:
- Auth: `POST /auth/register`, `POST /auth/login`, `GET /auth/profile`, `PUT /auth/profile`, `POST /auth/social`
- Product: `POST /products`, `GET /products`, `GET /products/:id`, `PUT /products/:id`, `DELETE /products/:id`
- Review: `POST /reviews`, `PUT /reviews/:id`, `GET /reviews?product=:id`
- Order: `POST /orders`, `GET /orders`, `GET /orders/:id`, `PUT /orders/:id/status`
- Push: `POST /push/register`, `DELETE /push/remove`, `POST /push/send-promo` (admin)

---

## 6) Definition of Done (Per Graded Item)

| Item | Done When |
|---|---|
| MP1 | Product/service full CRUD with camera/gallery photo upload |
| MP2 (15pts) | Register/login/profile update with photo |
| MP2 (20pts) | Google/Facebook OAuth working and verified server-side |
| MP3 | Verified purchase required before review; user can edit own review |
| MP4 (20pts) | SQLite cart persists on app restart; cleared after checkout |
| Term Test | Transaction creation → status update → push sent → tap opens order detail |
| Quiz 1 (15pts) | Search + category + price range filters working together |
| Quiz 2 | Promo push sent; tapping notification opens detail view |
| Quiz 3 | Redux slices drive product, order, and review data flows |
| Unit 1 | Drawer navigation UI integrated and presentation-ready |
| Unit 2 | JWT in SecureStore; push tokens saved on user; stale tokens cleaned up |

