## 7) Immediate Next 5 Tasks (Start Here)
1. Install missing frontend packages (`@react-navigation/drawer`, `expo-auth-session`, `expo-web-browser`, `expo-crypto`, `@react-native-async-storage/async-storage`).
2. Implement auth + JWT secure token storage + profile update (Milestone 1).
3. Implement product CRUD with Cloudinary upload (Milestone 2).
4. Implement SQLite cart persistence and restoration (Milestone 5).
5. Implement order checkout + status update + push notifications (Milestone 6).

---

## 8) Suggested Daily Delivery Discipline
- End each day with one merged, working vertical slice.
- Keep a `demo-ready` branch stable at all times.
- Record blockers in `docs/blockers.md`.
- Update this roadmap with completed dates as milestones are finished.